      "content": "it just feels like putting a bandaid on a broken bone. nothing actually gets better, it just stays heavy. i'm so tired of the fight. i keep wondering if there's even a point to trying to find a place where i fit if the world is just fundamentally built for people who aren't me. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
